Company Overview of DatChat, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
DatChat, Inc. provides a messenger service that enable users to send and receive encrypted messages that will self-destruct after a pre-set period of time. Its service is available through various Internet-enabled devices, including smart phones and tablets. The company was formerly known as Yssup, Inc. DatChat, Inc. was incorporated in 2014 and is based in New Brunswick, New Jersey.


