DatChat Messenger is much more than Self-Destructing messages and Hidden Encrypted Pictures
DatChat Messenger with our unique “Nuke” option allows you to completely eradicate both sides of a conversation on yours and the recipient’s phone.  Leaving absolutely no trace that the conversation ever took place.  Even the messages they sent are erased from their phone.

The DatChat Messenger makes sure that you always have complete privacy and control, especially after you hit send.  You can set a message to last forever, or automatically self-destruct after a certain amount of time or number of views.  Any time you want you can change your mind and wipe your messages off the recipient’s phone or give them more time to view them.  Additional features include the ability to protect your identity, prevent screenshots and hide encrypted pictures behind decoy images on the camera roll.









